Hybrid agent starting with:
  QUEUE_DIR= hybrid-queue
  RESULTS_DIR= hybrid-results
  WHITELIST= [
  'ls',
  'cat',
  'tail',
  'du',
  'df',
  'systemctl status',
  'journalctl -u',
  'npm run build',
  'npm ci',
  'rsync',
  'tar -czf',
  'service',
  'npm --prefix client run build',
  'npm --prefix client ci',
  'npm --prefix client run preview'
]
  DRY_RUN= false
  SECRET_REQUIRED= true
  MODE= poll

Usage notes:
 - Place files named <id>.cmd into the QUEUE_DIR.
 - Each .cmd file must start with a line: #hybrid-mode
 - Optional: include a line 'SECRET_TOKEN: <token>' if SECRET_TOKEN is set.
 - Results are written to RESULTS_DIR/<id>.result as JSON.

